videos.headline: BC's defense capitalizes with pick-six
videos.description: Jason Maitre picks off NC State QB Bailey Hockman for an 8-yard pick-six.

videos.headline: Bailey bursts through NC State defenders for 54-yard TD
videos.description: Boston College's David Bailey runs up the gut and breaks several tackles for a 54-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Bailey bounces to the outside and dashes into the end zone
videos.description: Boston College's David Bailey takes off for a long touchdown to extend the Eagle's lead to 24-3.

videos.headline: NC State throws TD on 4th down
